summaryText: On August 31st, several purchases were made including garters for 75 cents, belt ribbon for 25 cents, 2 pairs of stockings for 44 cents, a travelling basket for 2 dollars, gum arabia and myrrh for 13 cents, and sewing silk for 10 cents.
